"{\"uid\": \"news18.com-viral-meet-barbara-butch-the-dj-behind-the-controversial-last-supper-tableau-at-2024-paris-olympics-8982360.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Highlights of the 2024 Paris Olympics opening ceremony were C\\u00e9line Dion's performance and the lighting of the cauldron.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 60, \"end\": 71, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"C\\u00e9line Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, one performance has sparked a controversy.\", \"from\": 120, \"to\": 171, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In an image that some believed resembled Leonardo da Vinci's The Last Supper depiction of Jesus Christ and the twelve apostles, drag queens and performers lined a long table during a controversial tableau.\", \"from\": 172, \"to\": 377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 213, \"end\": 230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.326742754252642e-19, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 262, \"end\": 274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999565925480817, \"rank\": 4.3408945579111236e-05, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the event, some reportedly referred to the images as \\\"insulting to Christian people\\\" and \\\"mockery.\\\"\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 451, \"end\": 460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9989973792142749, \"rank\": 0.0008986928017814582, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The focal point of the Last Supper tableau was French DJ and LGBTQ activist Barbara Butch.\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 560, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"score\": 0.9999897744159937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Barbara Butch (@barbarabutch)    With a halo-shaped headdress and a fitted outfit, Barbara appeared in front of her DJ gear with a large group of dancers, drag queens and entertainers around her.\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"score\": 0.9999897744159937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}, {\"begin\": 678, \"end\": 685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Gordon\", \"score\": 0.904279642390894, \"rank\": 0.10382100980321665, \"text\": \"Barbara\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Gordon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Gordon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the midst of the increased attention, Barbara introduced herself on Instagram, writing, \\\"Hi my name is Barbara Butch, I am a Love activist, Dj and producer based in Paris.\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 966, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 833, \"end\": 840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Gordon\", \"score\": 0.904279642390894, \"rank\": 0.10382100980321665, \"text\": \"Barbara\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Gordon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Gordon\"}, {\"begin\": 863, \"end\": 872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1534874606765713e-23, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 898, \"end\": 911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"score\": 0.9999897744159937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}, {\"begin\": 960, \"end\": 965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999998303565, \"rank\": 1.6964341573975564e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My aim is to unite people, gather humans & share love through music for all of Us to dance & make our hearts beat at unisson!\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 1092, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Music sounds better with all of Us!\\\"\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1129, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Barbara advocates for several causes, such as acceptance of obese people and lesbian rights.\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1131, \"end\": 1138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Gordon\", \"score\": 0.904279642390894, \"rank\": 0.10382100980321665, \"text\": \"Barbara\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Gordon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Gordon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As part of her attempts to advocate fat acceptance, she produced a short movie called \\\"Extra Large.\\\"\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"French cultural magazine Telerama featured her in a nude photo on its cover in 2020, with the tagline, \\\"But why do we reject fat people?\\\"\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1462, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1350, \"end\": 1358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telerama\", \"score\": 0.9999999994613518, \"rank\": 5.319048995536939e-10, \"text\": \"Telerama\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telerama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telerama\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Later, the French Association of LGBTI Journalists recognised her work, and she was awarded the Out d'or 2021 (LGBTI Personality of the Year) title.\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Swipe Left For Next Video  The Paris-born personality began her career as a DJ in Montpellier, where she performed in clubs.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1695, \"end\": 1706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montpellier\", \"score\": 0.9174174349205717, \"rank\": 0.09001634150019991, \"text\": \"Montpellier\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montpellier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montpellier\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to IBTimes, she performed under the moniker Scratcheuse de gazon before going back to using her given name.\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1751, \"end\": 1758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Business_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IBTimes\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Business_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Business_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to reports, she resumed her profession in 2008 after returning to Paris, where she worked at establishments including Rosa Bonheur and La Machine du Moulin Rouge.\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 2028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1932, \"end\": 1937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999998303565, \"rank\": 1.6964341573975564e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1984, \"end\": 1996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosa_Bonheur\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3166229952731701e-27, \"text\": \"Rosa Bonheur\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosa_Bonheur\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosa_Bonheur\"}, {\"begin\": 2001, \"end\": 2011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Machine\", \"score\": 0.9999972885439472, \"rank\": 2.711462810560016e-06, \"text\": \"La Machine\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Machine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Machine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2023, Barbara made a cameo appearance as a celebrity judge on the French tv series Drag Race France.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2039, \"end\": 2046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Gordon\", \"score\": 0.904279642390894, \"rank\": 0.10382100980321665, \"text\": \"Barbara\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Gordon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Gordon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anne Descamps, a spokesman for Paris 2024, expressed regret for anyone hurt by the scene on Sunday.\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2233, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2139, \"end\": 2147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.